summary: The House Is  for followers and allows for people to use other mods like my home is your home.
descriptionHtml: This mod aims to bring your followers to live in one location. The entrance is located right under the bridge near Honning Brew Meadery. So as my first mod I created a big place for all my followers to live. There will only be storage like chest and cabinets. I do not know if I will put mannequins in or not.
author: Decoy237
